  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ad70852a75e640014c3f970",
      "text": "理解度",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041813,
      "updated": 1524041813
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc45",
      "text": "「理解度」という概念は、分母に「本に書かれている情報」を持ってくると、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc46",
      "text": "・100%理解するまで分母が不明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc47",
      "text": "・時間をかければ掛けるほど高い値になる傾向がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc48",
      "text": "という点から不適切な尺度だ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc4a",
      "text": "一方で「早く読みすぎて理解度が下がってしまった」などの表現は便利。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc4b",
      "text": "このギャップはどうやったら埋まるかなと考えていたが、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc4c",
      "text": "ここでいう「理解度」ってのは分母が「本に書かれている情報すべて」ではなくて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086baff09e00005ecc4d",
      "text": "「時間」だと考えるほうが適切なのではないか。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041835,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad70855aff09e00005ecc44",
      "text": "つまり「単位時間あたりに得られた理解の量」ではないか。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524041813,
      "updated": 1524041835
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad7086eaff09e00005ecc4f",
      "text": "",
